race.description: Tas Breeders Life Member Owen & Sandra Atkins Hcp (C1)
race.comment: STREETFIGHTER VEGA (3) was tried in rich company at Moonee Valley before the spell. Returns and did win first-up last time in work over 1200m at Hobart. Placed in both lead-up trials and will be naturally improved. The one to beat. RESPITE (1) is racing well, scoring two back at Devonport Synthetic before a nose defeat here over 1200m as a $5 equal favourite. Should park just off the speed and the longer sprint shouldn't bother. SKY EAGLE (5) progressed nicely last time, working home well beaten 1L here over 1220m. Is crying out for this distance and keeps the handy 2kg claim. SAY IT WITH WORDS (4) always puts in but needs to find more to be winning.
